ytechnic College: Awareness programme on eye care and free check up, A.Mohamed Yunus, college chairman, inaugurates, 9.30 a.m.Vetri Vinayaha College of Engineering and Technology, Tholurpatti: ISRO Space science exhibition, 10 a.m.Department of Information and Public Relations : Government exhibition, St.John’s Vestry Anglo Indian Higher Secondary School grounds, 4 p.m.Cauvery Matriculation Higher Secondary School and Cauvery Global School : Annual day, K. Balamurugan, Regional Passport Officer, Chennai, chief guest, 4.30 p.m.BHEL Matriculation Higher Secondary School : Annual Day, S.Gopinath, Executive Director, BHEL, Tiruchi, chief guest, 5.30 p.m.